  "description": "<p><strong>Job Summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Basic up to $2800 + AWS + VB</p></li><li><p>5 days work (8.15am - 5.30pm)</p></li><li><p>Location:<strong> </strong>Jurong East<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Coordinate internal & external training programmes (enrolment, logistics & attendance)</p></li><li><p>Liaise with stakeholders and training vendors on programme arrangements</p></li><li><p>Maintain training records, certificates & documentation (ISO/audit compliant)</p></li><li><p>Manage training enquiries, schedules, reminders & employee communications</p></li><li><p>Compile training materials, review e-learning content & analyse feedback</p></li><li><p>Support onboarding, internships, digitalisation initiatives & audits<br /></p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Min Diploma in HR or related field</p></li><li><p>Good interpersonal skills with a high level of accountability, initiative, and willingness to learn<br /></p></li></ul><p>For consideration, kindly submit your CV by clicking<strong> << APPLY Now >> </strong></p><p><< Only shortlisted candidate would be notified >><br /></p><p>Kiew Wai Kang | EA Reg No: R23112987</p><p>MTC Consulting Pte Ltd | EA License No: 15C7752</p>",
